For instance, if the mantra `tad vipr<193>so....' (eleventh mantra; ç
also <184>gveda 1.22.21) is repeated 100 times every day, the person ç
who does it will remember Lord Vi<218><207>u at the time of death.
A  brief  summary  of  the  twelve mantras (from the Taittir<200>ya ç
Sa<221>it<193>) may now be given: I praise the heroic deeds of Vi<218><207>u. ç
